front.title: •Aurra Sing
front.gametext: May use any 'stolen' lightsaber. Once per turn, may steal a lightsaber from an opponent's character just lost where present. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 while armed with a lightsaber).
front.lore: Bounty hunter. Former student of the Force. After failing her Jedi training, Aurra became known for hunting down and killing Jedi Knights.

rulings: Stolen lightsabers cannot be transferred to Aurra (unless they are actually capable of deploying on her).
